query:
SELECT v.id as video_id, v.fileId, v.url as video_url, v.fileKey as video_fileKey, f.id as file_id, f.url as file_url, f.fileKey as file_fileKey 
FROM videos v 
LEFT JOIN files f ON v.fileId = f.id 
LIMIT 10;
